{"tid":2441443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Now 政情冇人對稿? 瀨尿蝦同牛丸溝埋一齊","createTime":"2021-03-10T17:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T06:55:14.000Z","uid":13745,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"824e858ec5ba29c60c9edbe6e80b795871857a39","tid":2441443,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=426890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426890&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=d50e32f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426890&h=ddf7578a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=426890</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】國安法生效後，有民主派團體相繼解散，民陣亦面對威脅。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡《聯合時報》早前報道，民陣正被警方調查資金來源，若有證據來自外國或會違反國安法，有機會被取締，民陣有40多個團體參與，名單近日在網頁上刪除，街工在報道翌日就率先宣布退出。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡幾時有份報紙叫聯合時報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瀨尿蝦同牛丸溝埋一齊呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588b82fb752d2fa6b41f890029f7202fc19f4b00","tid":2441443,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"now 員工用百度search 唔到, 冇google 用呀ching"},{"pid":"32451ac50336af1a904f49aa36ff5d4e45c1fdc9","tid":2441443,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"聯合早報+海峽時報=聯合時報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735b54020f24505ec569fafc3b3c94398342edf1","tid":2441443,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":